net.sourceforge.js3tream
Class StdinOperation

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.js3tream.Operation
      net.sourceforge.js3tream.StdinOperation

public class StdinOperation
extends Operation

Read the java stdin stream, and write it's data to the S3 bucket. If the data will not fit into a single bucket object, then it will be split into bucket objects of size MAX_BUCKET_ENTRY_BYTES each.
